  "detailed_description": "Range is HOT! is a VR competition shooting simulator. Shoot your way through a variety of targets and courses to get the lowest time possible. Climb the leaderboards and hone your skills from the comfort of your home. Did we mention the ammo is free?<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>36 Multigun courses utilizing handgun, rifle, and shotgun shooting<br></li><li>10 Practical Shooting Classifiers<br></li><li>Trap and Skeet Practice<br></li><li>Static and Moving Targets<br></li><li>Scout and practice course sections to develop a strategy for maximum effectiveness<br></li><li>Outdoor ranges and indoor shoothouses<br></li><li>In-Game Tournament Events</li></ul><br><strong>Since entering Early Access, we've added:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30+ Courses <br></li><li>3 New Environments: Rocky Mountain Range, Warehouse, Night Range<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503590/extras/d0400402ec32ab5ac5028c4428140f77.avif?t=1658264115\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503590/extras/cebbd6009ac1245088edc5cb40b60c31.avif?t=1658264115\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503590/extras/3646fe991bd3cb83d7a2523e98256ac0.avif?t=1658264115\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br></li><li>7 New Firearms: O/U Shotgun, Bertino2011 Pistol, DaviDae320 pistol, Bearbelli Shotgun, Fossberg Shotgun, Grizlikov80 Rifle, SLAP17 Rifle<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503590/extras/67bf7f3640b59665f0912bed73ddb136.avif?t=1658264115\" width=600 height=207 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"